text: The Mercedes-Benz E-Class is a series of mid-size luxury cars manufactured by the German car maker Mercedes-Benz. The E-Class has been in production since 1953 and is one of the most important models in the Mercedes-Benz lineup. ==Versions== * W124 (1993) * W210 (1995) * W211 (2002) * W212/C207 (2009) * W213/C238 (2016) * W214/C236 (2023) ==Other websites== * Category:1960s automobiles Category:1970s automobiles Category:1980s automobiles Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles E-Class
